body:
Decode_raw_op test fails on big endian with an error "Unimplemented support for little_endian=true".
As per [comments](https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/pull/5450/#issuecomment-270173816), we have made changes in decode_raw and created a new PR for ongoing discussion on this.
